description:
In episode 612, Jack, Miles, Jamie and Anna are joined by Yo Is This Racist's Andrew Ti for the inaugural TDZ Movie Club to discuss The Goofy Movie!

FOOTNOTES:

  1. Mrs. Goof
  2. Gawrsh! Goofy’s entire family may be dead
  3. A Goofy Movie star reflects on film 25 years later: ‘Unlike any other project I’ve worked on’
  4. DuckTales Quietly Confirms A Goofy Movie Is Canon
  5. I Interned for Pauly Shore (and It Really Sucked)
  6. Things You Didn't Know About 'A Goofy Movie'
  7. WATCH: Mariposa De Coalcomán - Y La Bamba
